				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Facts: 
<br />

<br />
I typically clock 300-350 DPS casting on most mobs that take any non-trivial amount of time to kill. I have Discordant focus pieces and GoD Ancient. I do not have OoW nukes, nor do I have FoMM or HoF.
<br />

<br />
My pet typically clocks 70-110 DPS melee with Ritual Summoning.
<br />

<br />
Pet casting/proc damage has been previously reported as insignificant compared to 400 DPS and likely none on raid-level mobs (due to resists).
<br />

<br />
That puts my pet's damage at about 15-25% of my total damage.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Elementalist Itchyban of Veeshan</a>
