<br />
We get the best summoned pets in the game, but when it comes to mitigation and dps, they are at best only slightly ahead of other summoned pet classes.
<br />
 
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Our pet is only 40% of our dmg output  most ppl who whine about this want about a 30 -70% dps boost for our pets 40% of our dmg *30 % lacking =12 %  dps lower then we “should be at” (please notice the quotes)  be now keep in mind that we are a solo class ,  because we are not 100%-90% group dependent we should NOT bring as much to a group ( or raid for that matter ) as a rouge, cleric , enchanter war exc.
